long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Tab Browse extension brings a fresh look to your default Chrome New Tab page. With every Chrome browser or new tab launch, you will enjoy the abstract wallpapers.
Give your Chrome a new look with abstract wallpapers and set Tab Browse as your default search provider for Chrome.

Features:
- One fixed wallpaper: You may want a fixed wallpaper you always want to see, then just click on an image listed in the backgrounds section
- Search box: Search the entire web within the extension
- Quick Links: Quickly access to the most popular social media websites

Terms of Use: https://tabbrowse.com/tb-terms.html
Privacy Policy: https://tabbrowse.com/tb-privacy.html

By click on the «Add to Chrome» button in the top right hand corner and installing the Tab Browse extension, you are agreeing to install this extension, you are agreeing to our Privacy Policy, and you are agreeing to our Terms of Use. The extension will update your search settings and will change your New Tab search services provided by Tab Browse.
